Cell["\<\
The one way ANOVA shows that there is a significant difference between the \
means. We cannot find out between which classes yet. This would require \
multiple t-tests.
Lets move on to introduce another factor, the sex of the participants.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.980190491797964*^9, 
  3.980190596049869*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"40a290f9-ca76-4872-9ca5-\
4eae87d3fb89"],

